"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:41:04.000Z","msg":"通常訓4-6個鐘"},{"pid":"71f2ff89b3f840efc413317bd4e871d01ec05905","tid":793984,"uid":72963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:50:14.000Z","msg":"每日跑步 最少半個鐘<br />\n訓前一鐘 唔好掂電子產品<br />\n聽relax music + meditation <br />\n<br />\n你做得哂的話會有改善<br />\n利申 失眠幾年 近排已好轉"},{"pid":"8e78cc1503ddc9142bda5dc02bdff5bc5027b8e5","tid":793984,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143f286db22cdc26c066b4ee156153123ac6eb6d","tid":793984,"uid":87417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73e113f91a1c0e10a1f1842b3fee4ec8d72718d7","tid":793984,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T21:42:10.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T21:49:41.000Z","msg":"次次睇醫生都會講<br />\n佢就問我係咪有野煩或者有心事<br />\n但係明明日日做緊廢青<br />\n邊度有心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著次次都話依賴藥物唔好就放我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"做廢青 冇野做 身體保留太多精力冇地方發洩係失眠其中一個因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd4faf449cca71b8a325fe07ae0df1eda4adac1","tid":793984,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a59edcb534173e921798ab92b89518b6e2896c05","tid":793984,"uid":203721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T21:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n失左幾耐？ <br />\n因為咩因由？ <br />\n有無睇過醫生？<br />\n<br />\n短期既話 有無試過去萬寧買現成個啲？<br />\n我記得分兩隻長效同速效<br />\n前者要用水食後者係可以口含<br />\n主要好似係for 搭長途機或者有時差個啲人食<br />\n又列明唔會令你賴床唔知醒<br />\nSo far 我都無因為食佢個隻搞到遲到<br />\n<br />\n我自己初頭因為個排失戀<br />\n晚晚喊到赲都訓唔著 返工要擔錢銀無精神好麻煩<br />\n咁岩好似係高登睇到有巴絲咁岩開post介紹<br />\n我食個隻喊到赲就會訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過治標唔治本 試唔試自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你最好留意返自己情緒起伏有無問題<br />\n或者性格大改變  會唔會係情緒病影響到你？<br />\n<br />\n去一般診所睇醫生同佢講返<br />\n有懷疑既可以叫佢寫埋轉介信比你<br />\n<br />\n我自己就依然係為左同一個人<br />\n佢係最主要既導火線 <br />\n加埋自己返工壓力大 <br />\n唔食唔訓喊同喊<br />\n長時間返最小十一個鐘又要體力勞動<br />\n唔夠精神多甩漏壓力更加大<br />\n終於爆左煲 變左抑鬱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"咁宜家有冇好返啲？"},{"pid":"2bfd224a90084d1a9095a786444c5001e6e35a4a","tid":793984,"uid":18600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbe09ced947b0cfe04d5d899028e644dd7cc01b","tid":793984,"uid":69560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T21:57:25.000Z","msg":"你除咗失眠身體仲會唔會有其他唔舒服嘅地方？<br />\n我16至18歲日日都睇日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後撞咗車，去骨醫check 到原來係有啲骨移咗位壓住神經線搞到失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢由細到大個背脊都好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔知會搞到失眠<br />\n依家醫番好我就瞓得好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"求介紹"},{"pid":"7e47b90933aad7d26f84e964b1fc4ef25b70700a","tid":793984,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:19:58.000Z","msg":"戒j 、習慣定時早瞓同埋適量運動、尤其朝頭早要曬下太陽， 呢幾招最實際。"},{"pid":"100e58fcb061a36d272ffb17d3dc3752a219fb6a","tid":793984,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e47b90933aad7d26f84e964b1fc4ef25b70700a","tid":793984,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi